      <TR>
        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top' nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Abillister</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>CoB is Call of Bones, it is the lvl 34 HP>maan (lich) spell.  It is the first line of these that turns you into a skeleton which also has the added benefit of ultravision and on some mobs faction change.  </P><P>Ok next for spells...darkness, fear, send pet, DoT...that is normally the basic order, you can play around with it as you wish, but i recommend sticking with darkness first, fear can be a bit later though.  Oh also when you summon a pet target it (you can do so by clicking it or hitting F1 twice) and con it.  At lvl 4 with the lvl 4 pet you want it to be white or yellow, as you go up in lvl it will be blue.  Up till about lvl 12 you will be able to get yellow pets (i think at 12 you can get white).  After 12 always try and get a blue one.  in case you don't know, your pets can be different lvls, the only difference really being how hard tehy hit.  Also at this lvl give your pet 2h weapons and it will max hit more often.</P><P>I recommend, if you haven't, looking up the spell/pet guides on this site.  The spells all have little strategy tips on them.  Mostly though just play around with them and see what you like.  Also if you have a question in game look around for a higher lvl necro, they will normally help (if none are in your zone do something like<BR>/w all 58 60 necro  or if you have a specific spell question someone around your lvl in place of the 58 60, oh also before you ask be sure they aren't in some uber high zone and ask nicely...as long as you are nice about it you will almost always get an answer, and if they can't answer because they are on a raid they normally say so).  Also go to the newbie forum, raise the amount of posts you can see and see if you have any questions that have already been covered (or even use the search engine, just be sure to click the match any words button)</P><P><marquee><b><font=red> ABILLISTER "MONKEY" ABU-Povar</font></b></marquee><BR><marquee><a href="<a href="http://whiteangels.guildsofeq.com/MainFrame.asp" target="_blank">http://whiteangels.guildsofeq.com/MainFrame.asp</a>" target="_New">Sojourn's Talon</a></marquee></font></td>
